# content-ref.txt is per-branch state, owned by the upstream content bot.
# Branch merges must NEVER propagate it; each branch keeps its own pin
# (master tracks fpwiki-content@master, test tracks fpwiki-content@test).
# The "ours" merge driver is registered per-clone by scripts/setup-git.mjs
# (chained from package.json `postinstall`). See CLAUDE.md "Pitfalls"
# for the full rationale.
/content-ref.txt merge=ours
